				<outline text="I have not been able to find [[Guy Kawasaki]]'s &lt;a href=&quot;https://guykawasaki.com/remarkable-people/&quot;&gt;podcast&lt;/a&gt; feed. The usual tricks aren't working. Here's his Apple Podcasts &lt;a href=&quot;https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/guy-kawasakis-remarkable-people/id1483081827&quot;&gt;preview&lt;/a&gt; page. Usually if you give that URL to the &lt;a href=&quot;https://getrssfeed.com/&quot;&gt;GetRSSFeed&lt;/a&gt; app, it returns with the address of the [[RSS]] podcast feed. This is &lt;a href=&quot;https://podcastaddict.com/podcast/2467377&quot;&gt;where&lt;/a&gt; it took me. I &lt;a href=&quot;http://xmlviewer.scripting.com/?url=https://podcastaddict.com/podcast/2467377&quot;&gt;viewed the XML&lt;/a&gt;, and it shows me an HTML page? If anyone can figure out the URL of his podcast feed, please let me know. Thanks." created="Thu, 15 Jul 2021 13:12:07 GMT" type="outline"/>
