				<outline text="When we're successful with [[Tools for Thought]], you will be able to write beautiful rendering software, and have it work with *every* notetaking tool. Much as an RSS feed isn't for any specific news reader, they can all read every feed. We will do the same for idea processing tools. " created="Sun, 11 Jul 2021 17:04:43 GMT" type="outline"/>
				<outline text="Rick Smolan" created="Sun, 11 Jul 2021 23:26:22 GMT" type="outline">
					<outline text="Photo by &lt;a href=&quot;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rick_Smolan&quot;&gt;Rick Smolan&lt;/a&gt; of yours truly at a tech conference in 1991 (guessing). " created="Sun, 11 Jul 2021 23:26:28 GMT" inlineImage="http://scripting.com/images/2021/07/11/daveAtTechConf1991.png"/>
